            <title>[LU-1358] update to the latest redhat and centos kernels: kernel-2.6.32-220.13.1.el6</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1358</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;RedHat and CentOS have updated their minor version of the kernel to: kernel-2.6.32-220.13.1.el6&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Our Lustre builds are currently at 2.6.32-220.7.1&lt;/p&gt;</description>
